<p>
<note n="0650024" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0650024">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】寬治七年寫高山寺藏寺</note>
<note n="0650025" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0650025">叡＝眷【甲】</note>
